Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • Code.Map
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Buyable

    public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
implements Buyable
    An object that keeps track of which maps the team owns. Can be bought at the shop. If a map is owned the buttons will display the location names in the game environment.
